I was trying to add back the result check of apply-patch.
https://github.com/sonic-net/sonic-mgmt/blob/babe544009363cd33becdbbd73da73c0846b7b8d/tests/configlet/util/generic_patch.py#L204


Now `generic_patch_add_t0` will succeed but `generic_patch_remove_t0` won't.
By checking the result, it seems there is a conversion from uppercase to lowercase that results in the leafref failure
```
   "stdout_lines":[
====>#####NOTE: Where does it come of below line conversion? ######
      "converted ipv6 address to lowercase fc00::41~1126 with prefix /INTERFACE/Ethernet64| in value: /INTERFACE/Ethernet64|FC00::41~1126",
      "Patch Applier: Patch application starting.",
      "Patch Applier: Patch: [{\"path\": \"/QUEUE/Ethernet64|3\", \"op\": \"remove\"}, {\"path\": \"/QUEUE/Ethernet64|2\", \"op\": \"remove\"}, {\"path\": \"/QUEUE/Ethernet64|1\", \"op\": \"remove\"}, {\"path\": \"/QUEUE/Ethernet64|0\", \"op\": \"remove\"}, {\"path\": \"/QUEUE/Ethernet64|6\", \"op\": \"remove\"}, {\"path\": \"/QUEUE/Ethernet64|5\", \"op\": \"remove\"}, {\"path\": \"/QUEUE/Ethernet64|4\", \"op\": \"remove\"}, {\"path\": \"/PORT/Ethernet64/admin_status\", \"op\": \"remove\"}, {\"path\": \"/PORT/Ethernet64/description\", \"value\": \"fortyGigE0/64\", \"op\": \"replace\"}, {\"path\": \"/BUFFER_PG/Ethernet64|0\", \"op\": \"remove\"}, {\"path\": \"/BGP_NEIGHBOR/10.0.0.33\", \"op\": \"remove\"}, {\"path\": \"/BGP_NEIGHBOR/fc00::42\", \"op\": \"remove\"}, {\"path\": \"/PORT_QOS_MAP/Ethernet64\", \"op\": \"remove\"}, {\"path\": \"/BUFFER_QUEUE/Ethernet64|5-6\", \"op\": \"remove\"}, {\"path\": \"/BUFFER_QUEUE/Ethernet64|0-2\", \"op\": \"remove\"}, {\"path\": \"/BUFFER_QUEUE/Ethernet64|3-4\", \"op\": \"remove\"}, {\"path\": \"/DEVICE_NEIGHBOR_METADATA/ARISTA01T0\", \"op\": \"remove\"}, {\"path\": \"/DEVICE_NEIGHBOR/Ethernet64\", \"op\": \"remove\"}, {\"path\": \"/CABLE_LENGTH/AZURE/Ethernet64\", \"value\": \"0m\", \"op\": \"replace\"}, {\"path\": \"/ACL_TABLE/EVERFLOW/ports/8\", \"op\": \"remove\"}, {\"path\": \"/ACL_TABLE/EVERFLOWV6/ports/8\", \"op\": \"remove\"}, {\"path\": \"/INTERFACE/Ethernet64\", \"op\": \"remove\"}, {\"path\": \"/INTERFACE/Ethernet64|10.0.0.32~131\", \"op\": \"remove\"}, {\"path\": \"/INTERFACE/Ethernet64|fc00::41~1126\", \"op\": \"remove\"}]",
```
